        <ont:ISO15926_desc>A &lt;PUMP CASING&gt; is a &lt;CASING&gt; and a single wall surrounding the impeller. The suction and discharge nozzles form an integral part of the casing. Typically applied for centrifugal pumps</ont:ISO15926_desc>
