        <ont:ISO15926_desc>A &lt;PUMP IMPELLER&gt; is an &lt;ARTEFACT&gt; and a &lt;IMPELLER&gt; that forms part of a rotating assembly of a pump imparting kinetic energy to the liquid being pumped</ont:ISO15926_desc>
        <ont:ISO15926_name>PUMP IMPELLER</ont:ISO15926_name>
    </owl:Class>
    


